These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, soy-milk
6 different games are played: canasta, whist, monopoly, poker, chess, bridge
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
6. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person playing chess is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee  | iced-tea    | lemonade  | cola      | milk    |
| Game      | whist  | bridge | chess | canasta | poker | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
City: marseilles, miami, rome, hannover, venice, boston
6 different pets are kept: dog, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person traveling to boston is the owner of the mouse##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
9. the person traveling to marseilles is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| City   | marseilles   | venice | miami | boston | hannover     | rome  |
| Pet           | goldfish | goat    | dog      | mouse  | guinea-pig | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: skateboard, motorbike, subway, roller, jet-ski, snowmobile
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, british, chinese, colombian, german, polish
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the colombian is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the german##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the polish##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the british##1
7. the colombian is on the far right##1
8. the chinese is the person driving the roller##1
9. the person driving the subway is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Transport   | roller   | snowmobile   | jet-ski      | motorbike | skateboard  | subway   |
| Nationality   | chinese | polish | argentine | british   | german | colombian |

