.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, action, crime, drama, time-travel
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, country, disco, electronic, house, techno
 1. the fan of disco is the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the fan of country##1
 3. the fan of house is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 4. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 6. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
10. the person watching crime movies is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre         | crime | time-travel | disaster | drama | epic | action  |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | electronic  | disco  | classical | house      | country |

