.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, disco, dubstep, folk, indie, pop
There 6 different types of food: strawberry, banana, potato, cherry, broccoli, plum
1. the person eating plum is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the person eating banana is on the left of the fan of country##1
5. the person eating broccoli is the fan of pop##1
6. the fan of disco is on the right of the person eating potato##1
7. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
8. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
9. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | dubstep    | country | indie     | disco   | folk     |
| Food   | broccoli | banana | plum | potato | cherry | strawberry |

