.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, guinea-pig, horse, snake, turtle
The people have 6 different jobs:  doctor, project-manager, librarian, designer, scientist, musician
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the scientist is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the doctor##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the librarian##1
5. the owner of the horse is the musician##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the librarian##1
7. the doctor is on the left of the designer##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Pet         | dog       | turtle     | horse | guinea-pig | snake | chinchilla |
| Job   | project-manager | scientist | musician | librarian     | doctor  | designer       |

