4. the person driving the van is the librarian##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
6. the electrician is on the left of the librarian##1
7. the librarian is on the right of the electrician##1
8. the accountant is on the left of the security-guard##1
9. the librarian is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Job    | accountant | security-guard | scientist | electrician    | librarian | project-manager      |
| Transport   | ship   | bike     | bus      | subway | van           | snowmobile |

