.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
House: farmhouse, cottage, art-deco, ranch-style, townhouse, colonial
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: family, mystery, satire, thriller, western, zombie
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is the cottage house##1
4. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
6. the cottage house is on the far left##1
7. the colonial house is the person watching family movies##1
8. the art-deco house is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
9. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| House          | cottage | colonial   | townhouse  | art-deco    | ranch-style  | farmhouse |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | family | zombie | western | satire | thriller |

