.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-13::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  doctor, fisherman, nurse, paramedic, police-officer, writer
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, pall-mall, davidoff, old-henry, aristoff, tiparillo
1. the paramedic is the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the doctor is on the left of the writer##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the doctor##1
4. the doctor is the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the fisherman is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the fisherman##1
7. the nurse is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
8. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left##1
9. the writer is the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |       3        |     4     |     5     |   6    |
| Job         | nurse | fisherman | police-officer | paramedic | doctor    | writer |
| Cigar   | baccarat   | aristoff      | old-henry        | davidoff    | pall-mall | tiparillo  |

