4. the person eating papaya is on the left of the fan of indie##1
5. the person eating mango is on the right of the fan of funk##1
6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the fan of funk##1
8. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating mango##1
9. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |    4    |      5       |     6     |
| Food         | zucchini | raspberry | mango | grapefruit | papaya | cherry |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | funk      | jazz    | folk    | metal        | indie     |

