.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-17::.
6 different pets are kept: cat, goat, hamster, rat, snake, turtle
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, lemonade, iced-tea, milk, fanta
1. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the rat is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |    3     |    4     |    5    |       6       |
| Pet     | snake  | rat       | turtle   | cat      | hamster | goat          |
| Beverage   | milk | hot-chocolate | lemonade | 7up | iced-tea | fanta |

