.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, funk, house, metal, rock, salsa
There are 6 different nationalities: german, polish, indonesian, japanese, indian, chinese
1. the indonesian is on the right of the indian##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the japanese is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the indonesian is on the right of the indian##1
7. the japanese is on the right of the polish##1
8. the polish is on the right of the german##1
9. the german is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | salsa     | rock       | house  | metal | country    |
| Nationality     | chinese  | german | polish | japanese | indian  | indonesian |

 